'''石垣號海防艦'''（{{jpn|j=石垣|hg=いしがき|rm=Ishigaki|f=h}}）是二战中[[大日本帝国海军|大日本帝国海军]]的[[占守级海防舰|占守级海防舰]]一艘，她以千岛群岛为基地执行巡逻和护航任务。以击沉美国海军S-44号潜艇闻名（该艇于[[萨沃岛海战|萨沃岛海战]]中击沉了[[加古號重巡洋艦|加古號重巡洋艦]]）。

==服役==
[[File:USS-S-44-155a.jpg|thumb]]
1943年10月7日晚石垣号击沉了美国潜艇USS S-44 SS-155. 当时''S-44''在雷达上发现一个目标<ref name=fleet>{{cite web|title=FleetSubmarine.com|url=http://www.fleetsubmarine.com/ss-155.html|publisher=www.fleetsubmarine.com|accessdate=6 November 2012|archive-date=2013-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130703062400/http://www.fleetsubmarine.com/ss-155.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>她认为那是一条小货船并用甲板炮向之开火。<ref name=subsow>{{cite web|title=USS S-44 (SS-155)|url=http://www.subsowespac.org/world_war_ii_submarines/uss_s_44_ss_155.shtml|publisher=www.subsowespac.org|accessdate=6 November 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502235413/http://www.subsowespac.org/world_war_ii_submarines/uss_s_44_ss_155.shtml|archive-date=2014-05-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

